```

4. Close the `axis` and `tikzpicture` environments.

```latex
\end{axis}
\end{tikzpicture}
```

5. End your document.

```latex
\end{document}
```

Here's a complete example of how to use the `pgfplots` package to draw a simple bar graph:

```latex
\documentclass{article}
\usepackage{pgfplots}
\pgfplotsset{compat=newest}

\begin{document}

\begin{tikzpicture}
