\end{tikzpicture}

\end{document}
```

Compile this with `pdflatex` or an equivalent LaTeX compiler that supports `pgfplots`, and a bar graph should be displayed in the produced document. Note that you can customize the appearance of the bars and the chart extensively using other options and styles provided by the `pgfplots` package.

